{"tid":2118260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（阿均有嘢想講）跪求大家唔好離棄手足","createTime":"2020-07-21T10:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T02:13:17.000Z","uid":297672,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9725e399dda5ac147675b74a77cea450d4a2c159","tid":2118260,"uid":297672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:56:53.000Z","msg":"又係我，想為阿均轉達幾句話。<br />\n<br />\n日日如是嘅還押生活中，除咗拜山，收信係每日最期待最開心嘅事。佢收到好多同路人/和你寫筆友嘅信，對此十分感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但同時覺得因為訪問嘅光環令佢收多咗信，佢覺得內疚，甚至有啲後悔做咗探問，佢嘅本意只係為手足平反吓。<br />\n<br />\n正如佢講過<br />\n&ldquo;被捕嘅唔係數字，而係有血有肉嘅人&rdquo;<br />\n希望大家除咗上過報道有名有姓嘅手足之外，亦都唔好遺忘嗰一班默默付出而正身受牢獄之痛嘅佢哋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好想呼籲吓：<br />\n和你寫時，不妨多寫唔指名嘅信，讓更多牆內手足能夠收到溫暖慰問，俾手足知道佢哋並不孤單<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跪求大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef11fd64dbe892ddbcd933b085e6b35278e3576b","tid":2118260,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e638898bdd8b2b43dfc0b06b2898233cc4225d7e","tid":2118260,"uid":310970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T02:13:17.000Z","msg":"推唔到post <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}